# Import & Boundary Rules

## Package Imports
- Use package imports, not relative imports across packages
- Relative imports OK within the same package/lib

## Forbidden Imports
- packages/* must NEVER import from apps/*
- Feature packages must NEVER import from other feature packages
- presentation/ must NEVER import from data/ (go through domain/)
- domain/ must NEVER import from presentation/ or data/

## Import Order (enforced by directives_ordering lint)
1. dart: imports
2. package: imports (third-party)
3. package: imports (workspace packages)
4. relative imports

## Generated Files
- Import the source file, not the generated file
- The part directive handles generated file inclusion
